    {
      "chinese": "由於橋寬幾乎與車位標準寬度同寬，因此別名為「酒測橋」。橋的兩岸及橋本身繪滿部落的故事與文化，吸引著每一雙眼睛。",
      "ab": "ku thipala ikay taludru mahahamau ku thipala ku tapaisadrasadra ki didyusa, lakuni kisunagane ku takilekeleketa ki bava amiya, ku mababalrealreana ki taludru si taludru tinuzega ku lamaulai si kakwakudha ki cekele, thehepe bilibili ku tapumaca ki badhabadha.",
